# Compiled Code App bundles drift on every `npx power-apps push` (and on every
# `node scripts/pack-solution.mjs`). We track the metadata stub (.meta.xml) but
# ignore the bundle output — the live bundles are sourced from each app's
# `<app>/dist/` via push or via pack-solution, not from git.
src/CanvasApps/*_CodeAppPackages/

# Packed solution exports (zip artifacts of `pac solution pack`).
*.zip

# Build output of `node scripts/pack-solution.mjs`.
out/

# Temp scratch dir for `node scripts/pull-solution.mjs` exports.
.tmp-pull/
